Shell Aiming to Spend $200 Million on South African Shale Gas, I-Net Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-03-28T06:26:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/shell-aiming-to-spend-200-million-on-south-african-shale-gas-i-net-says.html
Royal Dutch Shell Plc (RDSA)  may spend as
much as $200 million exploring for shale gas in  South Africa ’s
Karoo region, Johannesburg’s I-Net Bridge reported, citing
Bonang Mohale, the chairman of Shell’s South African retail
